<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-70-0637 </DOCNO><TEXT>The activities of the Centre for Collection, Treatment and Storage ofLow-Level Radioactive Wastes (CRTADRBN) are presented. The objectiveof this centre is the final storage of radioactive waste and radiationsources generated by medicine, industry teaching and research. Safety,storage capacity and economy are considered in the design. The typesof treatment for liquid wastes are described and the containement systemis specified. (M.C.K.).</TEXT></DOC>